  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Sauté chopped onion and minced garlic in a saucepan until softened.",
    "Add ground lamb, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper. Cook until the lamb is browned, breaking it up into small pieces.",
    "Add bulgur wheat, kombu-cold-extract, and chopped parsley. Stir to combine and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a large bowl and stir in cottage cheese, shredded cheddar cheese, and vegan mozzarella.",
    "Cut the agave leaf into a pie dish shape and place it in the bottom of a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Fill the agave leaf with the bulgur mixture and cover with another agave leaf, pressing the edges to seal.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes, then reduce heat to 350°F (175°C) and bake for an additional 15 minutes.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool for 5 minutes before serving."
  ],
